				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">ok...my comp is far from new...
<br />
i understand that eq2 is quite adjustable as far as requirements are concerned...but i thought id ask to see if anybody out there is using what i have before i buy eq2.
<br />

<br />
i have
<br />
P4 2.0ghz
<br />
512 ram
<br />
GeForce 3
<br />

<br />
Yeah, i know i need a new comp, but $ is tight right now...
<br />
Is what i got enough to play eq2...and if its ok...do the graphics look like ass with the settings turned down for this setup?
<br />

<br />
Thx everyone</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
