			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ok you're definitely getting *some* performance hit based on file I/O.  The size of the hit depends on other factors.
<br />

<br />
But, that being said, set *both* initial size, and maximum size, to 1533.  This way, Windows won't be periodically resizing the page file (which is file I/O intensive).<br />_________________<br />EQ1:  Mujahid Mukhtaar - Arch Lich, Solusek Ro (Retired)
<br />
EQ2:  Mujahid Mukhtaar - Summoner, Mistmoore
